        <span class="bs-pill" style="--c: #f59e0b;">Tools</span>
        <span class="bs-pill" style="--c: #8b5cf6;">Agents</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="title" style="margin-top: 24px;">De ochtend-briefing.</h2>
      <p class="body" style="margin-top: 32px; max-width: 700px;">
        Tweehonderd mails per dag. Geen tijd om ze allemaal te lezen vóór de eerste vergadering.
      </p>

      <div style="margin-top: 56px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 22px;">
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: baseline;">
          <span style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-4); min-width: 64px;">01</span>
          <span style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--ink-2);">Koppel je mailbox, kies je terugkijkperiode.</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: baseline;">
          <span style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-4); min-width: 64px;">02</span>
          <span style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--ink-2);">Agent leest élke mail en trieert op type en prioriteit.</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: baseline;">
          <span style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-4); min-width: 64px;">03</span>
          <span style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--ink-2);">Schrijft een briefing: wat dringend is, wat kan wachten.</span>
        </div>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: baseline;">
          <span style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-4); min-width: 64px;">04</span>
          <span style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--ink-2);">Jij ziet in seconden wat telt, vóór je eerste koffie.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

