            </p>

            <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 11px;">
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 13px;">
                <span style="display: inline-block; width: 9px; height: 9px; border-radius: 999px; background: #dc2626; margin-top: 8px; flex-shrink: 0; box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(220,38,38,0.12);"></span>
                <span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--ink-2);"><b style="color: var(--ink);">BladPortal-storing</b> is actief. Klanten gemeld, los dit eerst op.</span>
              </div>
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 13px;">
                <span style="display: inline-block; width: 9px; height: 9px; border-radius: 999px; background: #dc2626; margin-top: 8px; flex-shrink: 0; box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(220,38,38,0.12);"></span>
