              <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 13px;">
                <span style="display: inline-block; width: 9px; height: 9px; border-radius: 999px; background: var(--accent-warm); margin-top: 8px; flex-shrink: 0; box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(180,83,9,0.12);"></span>
                <span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--ink-2);">Taken van <b style="color: var(--ink);">Koen Raes</b> (afwezig) tijdelijk overdragen.</span>
